    "body": "I was unable to build R on a laptop without the X11 header files. Apparently, R defaults to `--with-x` if you don't specify. This PR adds `--with-x` for `r+X` and `--without-x` for `r~X`.\r\n\r\nAlso converted to AutotoolsPackage and added the latest version of R.",
